---
import RollerLayout from '../../layouts/RollerLayout.astro'
---

<RollerLayout
  title="@randsum/roller - Advanced Dice Rolling Engine"
  description="The core RANDSUM dice rolling engine with powerful notation support and advanced modifiers"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div
    class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-randsum-950 via-randsum-900 to-randsum-800"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/grid.svg')] bg-center [mask-image:linear-gradient(180deg,white,rgba(255,255,255,0))]"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-24 sm:py-32 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-silver-50 sm:text-6xl"
        >
          <span
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-silver-300 to-silver-100 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
          >
            @randsum/roller
          </span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-silver-300">
          The core RANDSUM dice rolling engine. Advanced notation support,
          powerful modifiers, and lightning-fast performance for all your
          tabletop gaming needs.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
          <a
            href="/roller/docs"
            class="rounded-md bg-silver-600 px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-silver-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-silver-600 transition-colors"
          >
            Get Started
          </a>
          <a
            href="/roller/examples"
            class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-silver-300 hover:text-silver-50 transition-colors"
          >
            View Examples <span aria-hidden="true">‚Üí</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <div class="py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <h2
          class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-silver-50 sm:text-4xl"
        >
          Powerful Dice Rolling Features
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-silver-300">
          Everything you need for advanced dice mechanics in tabletop gaming
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-none">
        <dl
          class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3"
        >
          <!-- Advanced Notation -->
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <dt
              class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-silver-50"
            >
              <div
                class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-silver-600"
              >
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-6 text-white"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M17.25 6.75L22.5 12l-5.25 5.25m-10.5 0L1.5 12l5.25-5.25m7.5-3l-4.5 16.5"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              Advanced Notation
            </dt>
            <dd
              class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-silver-300"
            >
              <p class="flex-auto">
                Comprehensive dice notation with modifiers like drop lowest,
                rerolls, exploding dice, and more.
              </p>
              <p class="mt-6">
                <code class="bg-randsum-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-silver-100"
                  >4d6L</code
                >,
                <code class="bg-randsum-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-silver-100"
                  >2d20H</code
                >,
                <code class="bg-randsum-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-silver-100"
                  >3d6!</code
                >
              </p>
            </dd>
          </div>

          <!-- Custom Faces -->
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <dt
              class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-silver-50"
            >
              <div
                class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-silver-600"
              >
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-6 text-white"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M21 7.5l-9-5.25L3 7.5m18 0l-9 5.25m9-5.25v9l-9 5.25M3 7.5l9 5.25M3 7.5v9l9 5.25m0-9v9"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              Custom Faces
            </dt>
            <dd
              class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-silver-300"
            >
              <p class="flex-auto">
                Roll dice with custom faces for narrative outcomes, symbols, or
                specialized game mechanics.
              </p>
              <p class="mt-6">
                <code class="bg-randsum-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-silver-100"
                  >4d&#123;HT&#125;</code
                >,
                <code class="bg-randsum-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-silver-100"
                  >3d&#123;‚öîÔ∏èüõ°Ô∏èüèπ&#125;</code
                >
              </p>
            </dd>
          </div>

          <!-- TypeScript Support -->
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <dt
              class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-silver-50"
            >
              <div
                class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-silver-600"
              >
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-6 text-white"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              TypeScript Ready
            </dt>
            <dd
              class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-silver-300"
            >
              <p class="flex-auto">
                Full TypeScript support with comprehensive type definitions and
                excellent IDE integration.
              </p>
              <p class="mt-6">
                <span class="text-silver-400"
                  >Built with type safety in mind</span
                >
              </p>
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Quick Start Section -->
  <div class="bg-randsum-900/50 py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <h2
          class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-silver-50 sm:text-4xl"
        >
          Quick Start
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-silver-300">
          Get rolling in seconds with simple installation and intuitive API
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl">
        <div class="bg-randsum-950 rounded-lg p-6">
          <pre
            class="text-silver-100 overflow-x-auto"><code># Install the package
npm install @randsum/roller

# Start rolling
import &#123; roll &#125; from '@randsum/roller'

// Basic rolls
roll('1d20')     // Roll a d20
roll('4d6+2')    // Roll 4d6, add 2

// Advanced modifiers
roll('4d6L')     // Roll 4d6, drop lowest
roll('2d20H')    // Roll 2d20, keep highest
roll('3d6!')     // Exploding dice</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <div class="py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <h2
          class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-silver-50 sm:text-4xl"
        >
          Ready to roll?
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-silver-300">
          Explore the documentation and examples to get the most out of
          @randsum/roller
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
          <a
            href="/roller/docs"
            class="rounded-md bg-silver-600 px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-silver-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-silver-600 transition-colors"
          >
            Read the Docs
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/RANDSUM/randsum/tree/main/packages/roller"
            class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-silver-300 hover:text-silver-50 transition-colors"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            View on GitHub <span aria-hidden="true">‚Üí</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</RollerLayout>
